{"tid":696290,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解政府唔重建屯門公路","createTime":"2018-06-10T03:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T07:27:13.000Z","uid":137335,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a4173dd6c962dc984d3a2d52e36c08cc85dce010","tid":696290,"uid":137335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"唔係講緊早幾年做完果種加闊，隔音果種重建<br />\n<br />\n而係真正開條平坦 小彎嘅屯門至荃灣嘅公路<br />\n<br />\n有錢去起條回唔到本嘅高鐵<br />\n<br />\n點解冇聽過重建屯公？而且新界西北仲發展緊，人口愈黎愈多，屯公而家都已經收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家話起十一號幹線，開多條十一號幹線去大嶼山都冇用架，下年都有屯赤路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1feb352a92f4931c9ee80ea8494d385ca64da22c","tid":696290,"uid":42188,"like":35,"dislike":11,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T03:34:21.000Z","msg":"因為屯門人係低賤d<br />\n政府想懲罰屯門人，等佢地時時刻刻都飽受塞車帶來忍屎忍尿既辛苦，等佢地時常記得自己有幾低賤，想搬出九龍住既錢都冇"},{"pid":"6db7e4df3b927ca8357dc60de7b0bd59691a7e45","tid":696290,"uid":39632,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T03:36:20.000Z","msg":"除左係沿海邊開條新屯門公路 應該冇其他方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望佢開屯荃鐵路仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c458b1458a070a5f83cc4b46fd02bfe6fc060fa","tid":696290,"uid":30186,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1feb352a92f4931c9ee80ea8494d385ca64da22c","tid":696290,"uid":42188,"like":35,"dislike":11,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T03:34:21.000Z","msg":"因為屯門人係低賤d<br />\n政府想懲罰屯門人，等佢地時時刻刻都飽受塞車帶來忍屎忍尿既辛苦，等佢地時常記得自己有幾低賤，想搬出九龍住既錢都冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T03:38:03.000Z","msg":"我有錢都唔想搬 點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"bd70f585e08a045bd57e15e8f79068278cd9bce0","tid":696290,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c458b1458a070a5f83cc4b46fd02bfe6fc060fa","tid":696290,"uid":30186,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1feb352a